Tofas Turk Otomobil Fabrikasi AS ,
the Turkish unit of Fiat SpA, and Oyak-Renault, Renault SAâ€™s
local unit, plan record outputs this year,  Hurriyet  said.  Tofas plans to make 320,000 units and Oyak-Renault plans to
